</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Lighthouses" /><category term="Clouds" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The last of the storm clouds make for a beautiful sunset at the Pt. Vicente lighthouse. ポイント・ビセンテ 最後の嵐の雲が、ポイント・ビセンテ灯台の美しい夕日を演出。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2402_A7R07251-HDR-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2402_A7R07251-HDR-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Between Storms</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240207/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Between Storms" /><published>2024-02-07T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-02-07T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/playadelrey</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/240207/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
